      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "U. S. A.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "MAX KRENGEL",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Vice-Pres and Treas.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "ALLAN C. REVMAN",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "Secretary",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": ")II(",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "(8). Report to IFSB all reports and sightings in",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "your area. However, first put the sightings",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "before your group and let them judge whether",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "they are authentic or not.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "(9). Keep a record of all club members in your area",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "and their activities as far as IFSB is concerned.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "(10). Obtain if possible (merely a suggestion), a tape",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "recorder so that you can send actual voice to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "IFSB headquarters. In this way, I, as President,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "could send messages for you to play at your local",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "meetings. In the future I may even pay your city",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "a visit and attend one of your meetings.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "These are all merely suggestions for you to ponder over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "and if you decide to adopt any of them please consult with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "your Indiana Representative, Mr. Campbell. After you have",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "done this, get in touch with me at once.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "I sincerely hope that these suggestions will help you",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "in making some move as to what your local group will do.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "Forever Looking Up,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "Albert K. Bender",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
